{"tid":54294,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有屎（慎入）。求救。","createTime":"2016-12-25T12:08:27.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T11:30:34.000Z","uid":50508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eafc2afda2e5ca37af650564aeb60d0d4b606586","tid":54294,"uid":50508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T12:08:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CeB0428.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCeB0428.jpg&h=b87fef12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我隻狗連續五日屙咁既屎，有無巴絲打話俾我知佢咩事？<br />\n<br />\n佢得兩個半月大。一日兩餐。乾糧溝罐頭。<br />\n<br />\n轉食乾糧會好點嗎？"},{"pid":"cb51fd505bdae9e107fcacf7ff1040aec4aa72bf","tid":54294,"uid":39600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T13:39:13.000Z","msg":"唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇醫生<br />\n淨係知道狗狗兩三日都咁最好就要睇"},{"pid":"9bfb338cbc6e4dfda01eef13dbeacbcf8b068209","tid":54294,"uid":50508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T13:45:15.000Z","msg":"聖誕😢😢😢"},{"pid":"953bd3eea448163ddbb4f8e86b425fd78da1b5e9","tid":54294,"uid":22505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T14:51:54.000Z","msg":"睇獸醫啦<br />\n仲有咁細個係一日食4餐<br />\n少食多餐<br />\n唔好溝罐頭<br />\n乾糧要浸淋先好比佢食"},{"pid":"e45b9de3702857e28612168e602c7833a8379bca","tid":54294,"uid":8598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T15:02:53.000Z","msg":"狗仔焦慮就會屙呢種屎<br />\n<br />\n係咪跟你返咗屋企無幾耐？如果佢有籠，等屋企人準備休息時掟佢入籠瞓，等佢知道個籠係佢保護所"},{"pid":"fddfd169d3a73e25ecfe08fb17f03877e50d6673","tid":54294,"uid":50508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:13:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>狗仔焦慮就會屙呢種屎<br />\n<br />\n係咪跟你返咗屋企無幾耐？如果佢有籠，等屋企人準備休息時掟佢入籠瞓，等佢知道個籠係佢保護所</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有籠啊。<br />\n<br />\n黎左一星期啦。"},{"pid":"7fe60e2869a97cf185f2e8bda6bf25cd7ef1bc3f","tid":54294,"uid":12614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:16:11.000Z","msg":"Gg<br />\n我以前隻狗仔又係番左